== External links==
The long-term research project [[Text Database and Dictionary of Classic Mayan|Text Database Dictionary of Classic Mayan]] is working on a list of [http://mayawoerterbuch.de/?cat=202&lang=en Archaeological Sites with Maya Inscriptions] that is constantly growing. The list is sorted by site name, and primarily encompasses the archaeological sites in Mesoamerica where Maya hieroglyphic inscriptions have been discovered and verifiably documented over the course of archaeological survey and excavations.
