'''Marie-Galante Passage''' (''in french'':'''Canal de Marie-Galante''') is a strait in the [[Caribbean]]. It separates the island of [[Marie-Galante]], from [[Guadeloupe]] island and [[Îles des Saintes]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://fr.mapatlas.org/Guadeloupe/Chenal/Canal_de_Marie_Galante/1681/carte_routi%C3%A8re_et_satellite |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2011-12-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120426061343/http://fr.mapatlas.org/Guadeloupe/Chenal/Canal_de_Marie_Galante/1681/carte_routi%C3%A8re_et_satellite |archivedate=2012-04-26 |df= }}</ref>
